.Dd $Mdocdate$
.Dt ORT-AUDIT 1
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm ort-audit
.Nd audit ort role access
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm ort-audit
.Ar role
.Op Ar config...
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
utility accepts
.Xr ort 5
.Ar config
files, defaulting to standard input,
and audits all access available to
.Ar role .
.Pp
It outputs the role's access to the data and operations available (if
any) to each structure.
.Pp
This tool is still experimental.
